# shadcn instructions

- Use the latest version of Shadcn to install new components, like this command to add a button component:

```bash
bunx --bun shadcn@latest add button
```

# Shadcn Components Usage Rule

- Always use official Shadcn components whenever they cover the needed functionality or can be combined to solve the requirement, instead of building similar components from scratch. This ensures consistency, maintainability, and faster development.

